{"title":"祖国，振兴的时刻！——献给党的十二大的歌","authors":["张学梦"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，振兴的时刻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给党的十二大的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张学梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心熔化了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成一团火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅来自马丁炉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喉咙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才三千度炽热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论作为工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出入金属与电的蜂巢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论作为诗人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在情怀上颠颠簸簸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论白昼，理念统辖梦幻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或黑夜，梦幻自由的时刻……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要一想到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一想到你呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方地平线上的太阳："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那卵黄一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻颤动的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感情的核风暴啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就撞击胸膛的栅栏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗的雷霆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就滚向喉舌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱吧，遵照心髓的命令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锤子的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步枪的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵性的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们在最高意念的广场集合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们合唱，让我们交响——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨动钨丝一样耀眼的旋律："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏在大地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏在北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左前胸第五肋的间隙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压扁耳廓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那隆隆沉雄的地声是什么？是什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是母亲的心音——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴中国！振兴中国！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过死难烈士的墓园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我聆听到肃穆松柏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转述的嘱托；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带着景慕与迷惘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拜谒过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的长者；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我访问了骑木马的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和杜鹃花般的红领巾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我偷袭过青春的胸臆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侦察过装甲的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切过千百万人的脉搏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生的与死的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同一个心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同一个呼声——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴中国！振兴中国！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔚蓝的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷雨在呐喊吟哦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广袤的大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野渴盼得焦灼……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十万万大军的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄赳赳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共振着同一个节拍——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴中国！振兴中国！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我高歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你的苦恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你的欢乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让夜莺们去唱吧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那爱的苦辣酸甜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个人命运的莫测"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋雨淋浸的无名惆怅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小花欲放的春梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和枯草的抖索……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要跃上百米高炉的炉台、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃上火力发电厂烟囱的尖顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗渍斑斑的帽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在诗坛的高音部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把最嘹亮的那根心弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋力弹拨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着湿漉漉的朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着新世纪的风玫瑰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着确定不移的目标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌咏的下颌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅歌唱葛洲坝工程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅歌唱远程试验火箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅歌唱新竖的球罐、蒸馏塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅歌唱获奖的科研成果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅歌唱呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你活泼的思维"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理智的激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现状的突破"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中央委员们眉宇间的思虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思虑的书记处的灯火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱厂长的牢骚和苦闷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱清不完的问题、矛盾、纠葛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱！歌唱你艰难的步履"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂奋的拚搏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为，我晓得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有在这产前阵痛中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才会娩出一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代化的中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我确曾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悭吝过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象小贩悭吝他的糖果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾可耻地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象交易那样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支付过劳作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我不写忏悔录，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我顿悟过来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将用三倍的努力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥补昨天的过错。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，祖国，现在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请给我满负荷的工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿去战胜零下四十度的严寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿去经受零上一千度的酷热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿每天消耗七千卡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天完成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天的定额。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我去掘煤、炼钢、纺织、采油、淘金……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你的复兴和荣光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘愿不休止地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡劳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充实我的生活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊祖国，全都属于你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要儿子的什么？……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道黄色的迎春花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到时候自然就开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我们蓝图上的楼厦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不会瑞雪般降落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么动起来吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被爱国主义牵动的肌肉和骨骼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心熔化了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成一团火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成一首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在钢轨上滚动的诗歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一颗小星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自马丁炉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自内燃机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自金属铀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公民的职责。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在你怀里悄悄升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也将在你怀里悄悄睡去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，当在岗位上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的时候我不是贪婪的“黑洞”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是一块褐煤、一旅作功的电荷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一个心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激励着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象千千万万建设者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象历史的必然性——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴吧，祖国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴吧，祖国！！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}